Welcome to smart comfort with Westinghouse! Control your Westinghouse devices from anywhere with simple voice commands. 
Before you begin, make sure you have compatible Westinghouse devices and an active account in the Westinghouse Mobile app, then connect Alexa to your devices in a few simple steps:
1. Log in your "Westinghouse" app;
2. Configure our devices in "Westinghouse" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "Westinghouse" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the air conditioner.
Alexa, turn off the air conditioner.
Alexa, turn on the light.
Alexa, turn off the plug.
